Crash Recovery Algorithm: {
  shape: sequence_diagram

  Startup -> Check Journal: Begin recovery process
  Check Journal -> Validate Header: Journal exists
  Validate Header -> Read Page Records: Header valid
  Read Page Records -> Verify Checksums: Records read
  Verify Checksums -> Write Pages: Checksums valid
  Write Pages -> Sync: Pages written
  Sync -> Delete Journal: Sync complete
  Delete Journal -> Startup: Recovery complete
}